c394f1ddab837a44032c85","tid":1593533,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"照過胃鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同腸鏡唔同  唔需要飲瀉藥<br />\n但係好似要戒口<br />\n到時條友會噴啲嘢落喉嚨做局部麻醉<br />\n然後就慢慢塞條管入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣時我唔小心梗親  咳到勁唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8943ac582f3682306ab677595a7c89bbba5d3fd","tid":1593533,"uid":276080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e617e72a66cf0a51612b8db89f0e9c97f826b9df","tid":1593533,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29ead88c862e89510975391b4cbb0fbd32edc74d","tid":1593533,"uid":276080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"照過但好似入去照個陣瞓著咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醒個陣已經喺病房只喺喉嚨有啲痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"咩事照<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"之前肚痛到一日暈三次，喺急症等完一輪話唔知咩原因⋯<br />\n話可能喺胃抽筋，但都可能喺其他原因，然後就話check清楚好啲，之後就安排我照腦照心同照腸胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似乜都照過哂但都喺冇原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1146898b42710c5f4b6ef08116b52abda92c2a","tid":1593533,"uid":235074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"診所照過，唔知點解成日胃抽筋"},{"pid":"7acf93b00190e2aa594e2e0b2e1664e8394bf1fa","tid":1593533,"uid":27077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"我記得排我之前個女人照完  拎住張紙巾 抹下個嘴角,好從容咁出返嚟<br />\n跟住到我照既時候,反咗幾次胃 醫生不停叫我放輕鬆 用鼻呼吸"},{"pid":"60976ec050078c977e9e9f5a6c6883deb169e5e5","tid":1593533,"uid":27077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得排我之前個女人照完  拎住張紙巾 抹下個嘴角,好從容咁出返嚟<br />\n跟住到我照既時候,反咗幾次胃 醫生不停叫我<span style=\"color: red;\">放鬆啲</span> 用鼻呼吸</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e3afa2ca5109537d5c3f8010493fa4f6bef7aa33","tid":1593533,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"個個照胃 冇人照腸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eefa3102aaa54aeb4b489f569d5e1eda33606ed","tid":1593533,"uid":188484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"腸鏡/胃鏡基本上都係出去照，政府要等你好嚴重先會幫你照，胃鏡仲要唔會全麻，你會好辛苦。<br />\n腸鏡2年前係中環某棟醫生大廈照過，好似6,7蚊。照前頭幾日食流質嘢，前一日就飲瀉水，瀉5,6次應該差唔多瀉晒。照當日入去打支針就瞓著咗，醒返就照完。"},{"pid":"80e6b14ee7837437ddb065d83db496887ca63ddc","tid":1593533,"uid":188484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eefa3102aaa54aeb4b489f569d5e1eda33606ed","tid":1593533,"uid":188484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"腸鏡/胃鏡基本上都係出去照，政府要等你好嚴重先會幫你照，胃鏡仲要唔會全麻，你會好辛苦。<br />\n腸鏡2年前係中環某棟醫生大廈照過，好似6,7蚊。照前頭幾日食流質嘢，前一日就飲瀉水，瀉5,6次應該差唔多瀉晒。照當日入去打支針就瞓著咗，醒返就照完。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:56:50.000Z","msg":"6,7千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c48228f8349ef37a2e3fd236ca06a4c1ed480a2","tid":1593533,"uid":196758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"628065c1020162ca36b44f7d81f791712de2441f","tid":1593533,"uid":27077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fc5c33970780a08061d872b2f97b16070edba0c","tid":1593533,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f242ca3c74354eb1130386b335e8222f30157121","tid":1593533,"uid":27077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"長時間持續胃痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"醫生點講？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"照完話 乜事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:59:43.000Z","msg":"我上年照完無事<br />\n而家又胃病返<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc2c1246407e5d83d45f191ab2983de51249792","tid":1593533,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"18歲嗰陣照過胃鏡，想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咩事都係唔好照"},{"pid":"262aba1b8057ee4e44ee20c173ee826d4816a88c","tid":1593533,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"胃 大腸 小腸都照過晒<br />\n<br />\n胃鏡 <br />\n中學嗰陣經常胃痛<br />\n一肚餓就痛 食飽就冇事<br />\n照完結果係十二指腸潰瘍<br />\n照之前亂咁食咗啲消炎藥 照嗰陣已經復原<br />\n<br />\n大腸<br />\n畢業後經常肚痾<br />\n醫生排除所有可能性決定照腸鏡睇下咩料<br />\n發現有部份位置發炎<br />\n<br />\n小腸<br />\n照完大腸照埋小腸 小腸都有局部發炎<br />\n最後確診克隆氏症<br />\n<br />\n胃腸冇乜特別，係咁想嘔既感覺<br />\n大腸鏡都冇乜印象，因為我怕痛所以醫生打多咗鎮靜劑，隱約聽到聲，全程瞓著咁濟<br />\n小腸都係打顯影劑落血管，感覺到啲血管超熱，瞓喺枱度影幾張CT就完<br />\n<br />\n希望樓豬你身體健康"},{"pid":"7011e9cbc1152b651db8278affb5fc73108b09e4","tid":1593533,"uid":104135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23482416b2a4a8a53ac5b1f4297e5021291247f5","tid":1593533,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73303cf678217f01f0d804e0f2bfb5ae80e06997","tid":1593533,"uid":104135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"聽朝照"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:25:25.000Z","msg":"係唔係飲緊瀉水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:27:12.000Z","msg":"無 不過禁左食"},{"pid":"6aaa0ab900a29501306c9bc169f473a26f0d51ab","tid":1593533,"uid":104135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:50:17.000Z","msg":"照完了"},{"pid":"97354958eed120ecbb99fae727aa80b43f948b22","tid":1593533,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aaa0ab900a29501306c9bc169f473a26f0d51ab","tid":1593533,"uid":104135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime